tfg.grapplemod.downgrades.motor:
Disables the Motor Upgrade, returning the original motor.
Only works if you use the same type of motor as before.
tfg.grapplemod.upgrades.smart_motor: Enables the Smart Motor Upgrade, requires a Motor to be installed.
tfg.grapplemod.downgrades.smart_motor: Disables the Smart Motor Upgrade, can be removed with the Motor already uninstalled. Returns the Basic Electronic Circuit
